title: Junk food is linked to both moderate and severe psychological distress

title_detail.value: Junk food is linked to both moderate and severe psychological distress

summary: The study revealed that California adults who consumed more unhealthy food were also more likely to report symptoms of either moderate or severe psychological distress than their peers who consume a healthier diet.
